00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:30,320
 Walker had held many top jobs such as 15 years

536
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:32,960
 as the President of Penn State University.

537
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:34,760
 He was Chairman of the Board of the Institute

538
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:37,560
 for Defense Analysis, the top military think tank used

539
00:32:37,560 --> 00:32:39,040
 by the Department of Defense.

540
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:41,320
 He was Chairman of the National Science Foundation.

541
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:43,240
 He was Executive Secretary of the Research

542
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:47,240
 and Development Board and headed the Navy's Applied Research Lab

543
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:49,720
 at State College, Pennsylvania.

544
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:52,400
 In discussions with more than half a dozen researchers

