00:43:57,120 --> 00:43:59,800
 Among those nations that have conducted some kind

768
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:02,960
 of official UFO research besides the United States

769
00:44:02,960 --> 00:44:06,120
 and South America, which have been dealt in previous sessions,

770
00:44:06,120 --> 00:44:10,120
 we can mention Russia, the United Kingdom, France, Belgium,

