00:44:14,960 --> 00:44:18,000
 and New Zealand to cite a few.

773
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:20,880
 We have with us experts that will discuss

774
00:44:20,880 --> 00:44:24,440
 or had just discussed some of these countries like Italy,

775
00:44:24,440 --> 00:44:28,320
 the UK, Canada, and China, but no representatives

776
00:44:28,320 --> 00:44:29,800
 from the other nations.

777
00:44:29,800 --> 00:44:31,760
 So I will cover briefly the history

778
00:44:31,760 --> 00:44:33,160
 of official investigations

779
00:44:33,160 --> 00:44:36,920
 of two particularly important countries, France and Russia,

780
00:44:36,920 --> 00:44:41,160
 which have a rich amount of material in this field.

781
00:44:41,160 --> 00:44:44,200
 Let's start with France, a country that has one

782
00:44:44,200 --> 00:44:48,440
 of the oldest, continuous, and most rational approaches

783
00:44:48,440 --> 00:44:50,200
 to the UFO problem.

784
00:44:50,200 --> 00:44:54,160
 Some military investigations in France go back to the '50s,

785
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:57,800
 but the current program really took off in the mid-'70s

