985
00:55:24,600 --> 00:55:28,000
 by cosmonaut Major General Vladimir Kovalyonok

986
00:55:28,000 --> 00:55:32,600
 from the Salyut 6 space station on May 5, 1981.

987
00:55:32,600 --> 00:55:36,400
 The sighting of a pulsating round object,

988
00:55:36,400 --> 00:55:38,160
 which resembled a melon--

989
00:55:38,160 --> 00:55:39,560
 that's his quote--

990
00:55:39,560 --> 00:55:43,520
 and then became like a barbell and didn't resemble

