00:55:46,440 --> 00:55:49,800
 was admitted on the record in a videotaped interview

993
00:55:49,800 --> 00:55:52,400
 by the cosmonaut many years later.

994
00:55:52,400 --> 00:55:55,640
 Another cosmonaut, Major General Pavel Popovich,

995
00:55:55,640 --> 00:55:59,320
 even became, at one point, the president of the All Union

996
00:55:59,320 --> 00:56:01,440
 Ufology Association of the Commonwealth

997
00:56:01,440 --> 00:56:03,240
 of Independent States.

998
00:56:03,240 --> 00:56:06,880
 A quote from a 1992 paper by General Popovich

999
00:56:06,880 --> 00:56:10,560
 provides an appropriate ending to this brief presentation.

1000
00:56:10,560 --> 00:56:13,920
 He wrote, quote, "The UFO sightings

1001
00:56:13,920 --> 00:56:17,720
 have become the constant component of human activity

1002
00:56:17,720 --> 00:56:20,880
 and require a serious global study.

1003
00:56:20,880 --> 00:56:24,640
 In order to realize the position of man on Earth

1004
00:56:24,640 --> 00:56:28,060
 and in the universe, ufology, the scientific study

1005
00:56:28,060 --> 00:56:30,760
 of the UFO phenomenon, should take place

1006
00:56:30,760 --> 00:56:35,200
 in the midst of other sciences dealing with man and the world."

